    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You are wearing medium or heavy armor.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Your armor protects you from the deadliest hits. Each time you're critically hit while wearing the required armor, attempt a @Check[type:flat|dc:14]. On a success, it becomes a normal hit.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Special</strong> If your armor has a fortification rune, you roll only one @Check[type:flat|dc:12] or @Check[type:flat|dc:10] if it's a greater fortification rune.</p>"
